        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Vertical</h4>
        <p>The <em>Vertical</em> orientation can be used on desktop or tablet if the content within needs to be positioned on the right side of the component instead of underneath. Alternatively, it can also be used on mobile if the horizontal orientation has more steps or text labels with more words.</p>

        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/alert-vertical-orientation.svg' | url }}" alt="Vertical orientation alert">

