    {% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

        <h4>Too many or too few steps</h4>
        <p>Do not use too many or too few steps, there should be between three and five steps visible.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-1.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 1" style="--inline-img-max-width: 698px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Usage on mobile</h4>
        <p>Do not use the horizontal orientation with lots of steps or long text labels on mobile, switch to the vertical orientation instead.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-2.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 2" style="--inline-img-max-width: 360px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Validation</h4>
        <p>Do not use the <em>Error</em> step icon for any <strong>previous</strong> steps, a user cannot proceed to the next step without resolving any errors first nor can they go back to resolve any errors and then continue.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-3.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 3" style="--inline-img-max-width: 687px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Text labels</h4>
        <p>Do not use Progress steps without text labels, color or icons alone cannot be used to represent step position or validation if a user is colorblind or uses assistive technologies like a screen reader.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-4.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 4" style="--inline-img-max-width: 687px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Carousel</h4>
        <p>Do not use Progress steps as an image carousel without including other types of content.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-5.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 5" style="--inline-img-max-width: 687px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

        <h4>Tabs</h4>
        <p>Do not use Progress steps as <em>Tabs</em> even though they seem like similar components. Progress steps are used for guiding a user through a task by displaying sequential steps and instructional content.</p>

        {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
        <div class="inline-flex centered">
        <img src="{{ '/assets/progress-steps/progress-steps-best-practice-6.svg' | url }}" alt="Progress steps component best practice 6" style="--inline-img-max-width: 687px;">
        </div>
        {%- endcall %}

    {%- endcall %}

